t but the pets are doing the same, which is not bad really, but i find it impossible to sit and med for more than a a couple ticks without risking losing my pet, and that does not provide me with much mana at all.<br><br>I just dinged 53 last night soloing, again. Ever since i reached 50 it was like running face first into a wall. Unable to find a group, I don't think its me and i have heard other mages are having the same problems that i have= we have nothing unique to offer a group and most other classes see our pets as a death sentence at worst and a XP sponge at best.<br><br>I apologize if this seems like a rant but I am very angered by the treatment mages have been recieving at the hands of VI lately as i see it.<br><br>Am I missing something? is there something i am forgetting or does it seem like 50+ there is just no use for Mages. I am proud of my class and enjoy the fact that with me and my pet i can dish out obscene amounts of damage.<br><br>i wanted to post this to get feedback from the rest of the Mage community and see if maybe there was something i was missing or if my perception of our class getting sh!t on was accurate.<br><br>Thank you.<br><br>Aazzamar Spellfizzler <p>Hunt with honorFight with prideDie with style</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/uraslinstormchaser.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raslin Stormchaser</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/13/02 4:06:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=58.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why does VI hate us so?</span><hr size=1> Verant is looking at the 50+ problems with Mages, all i can say is watch the space. <p><CENTER><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=57265"> R